ation a business carries with everything they do. While a logo, typefaces and color schemes are super important, they\'re only a fraction of what it takes to create a great brand.\r\n\r\nWe compile everything – your name, mission statements, the products and services you provide, and how you deliver them to create a specific image in your target market\'s mind.\r\n\r\nIt\'s the perceived image of your company, combined with an emotional connection that motivates your audience to choose you above all the rest.\r\n<h5><span style=\"color: #000000;\">RELATED PROJECTS:</span> <a title=\"LifeSpace\" href=\"http://getthepeople.com/lifespace\">LifeSpace</a>, <a title=\"PrimoMaestro Italia\" href=\"http://getthepeople.com/primomaestro-italia/\">PrimoMaestro Italia</a>, <a title=\"She Creates Change\" href=\"http://getthepeople.com/she-creates-change/\">She Creates Change</a>,<a title=\"Nov8rix\" href=\"http://getthepeople.com/nov8rix/\"> Nov8rix</a>, <a title=\"Media Weapon\" href=\"http://getthepeople.com/media-weapon\">Media Weapon</a> [/column]</h5>\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<h2> PROGRESSIVE WEB DESIGN</h2>\r\n<div class=\"intro\">Your website is the single greatest opportunity for your business to interact with the world and declare your online presence.</div>\r\nYour website allows you to communicate powerful messages that can differentiate your brand from the rest. This is a big friggin\' deal. All your marketing and communication efforts lead back to this one spot. So while we craft strategic plans and are serious about premium design, creating websites that can transform your business and relationships is what makes us tick.\r\n\r\nIt\'s the experience your website provides that stays with visitors. Whether it\'s pushing your brand to the next level, increasing sales, building relationships, or bringing a new business to market, pushing the edge with your website is your best chance at achieving your online goals.\r\n<h5>RELATED PROJECTS:<a title=\"LifeSpace\" href=\"http://getthepeople.com/lifespace\"> LifeSpace</a>, <a title=\"PrimoMaestro Italia\" href=\"http://getthepeople.com/primomaestro-italia/\">PrimoMaestro Italia</a>, <a title=\"She Creates Change\" href=\"http://getthepeople.com/she-creates-change/\">She Creates Change</a>,<a title=\"Nov8rix\" href=\"http://getthepeople.com/nov8rix/\"> Nov8rix</a>,  [/column]</h5>\r\n[column width=one-third-last ]\r\n<h2>CREATIVE STRATEGY</h2>\r\n<div class=\"intro\">Without a solid strategy your end result ends up patch work and afterthoughts. Strategy before design turns visions into real solutions.</div>\r\nStrategic thinking and creative insights are the nuts and bolts of our shop. We partner directly with you and get to the heart of your marketing goals and challenges to create short-term wins and long-term road-maps.\r\n\r\nNailing down a proper strategy can lead to improved reputation, increased consumer loyalty and greater profitability. Move ahead without one, and problems could occur down the road if competitors do a better job of it than you do.\r\n\r\nWe\'ll stick to this game-plan every step of the way, constantly refining and upgrading how we intend to execute and deliver effective user experiences.\r\n<h5>RELATED PROJECTS:<a title=\"LifeSpace\" href=\"http://getthepeople.com/lifespace\"> LifeSpace</a>, <a title=\"PrimoMaestro Italia\" href=\"http://getthepeople.com/primomaestro-italia/\">PrimoMaestro Italia</a>, <a title=\"She Creates Change\" href=\"http://getthepeople.com/she-creates-change/\">She Creates Change</a>,<a title=\"Nov8rix\" href=\"http://getthepeople.com/nov8rix/\"> Nov8rix</a>, <a title=\"Media Weapon\" href=\"http://getthepeople.com/media-weapon\">Media Weapon</a> [/column]</h5>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"intro\" style=\"text-align: left;\">AREAS OF EXPERTISE + KEY SERVICES</div>\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Brand Strategy\r\n</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Brand Voice</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Positioning</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Visual Identity</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Messaging Strategy</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Logo Design</span>[/column]</h6>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Web Design</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Development</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">E-commerce</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Search Engine Optimization (SEO)\r\n</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Social Media Integration</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Content Management System</span>[/column]</h6>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[column width=one-third-last ]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Content Development</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Online Marketing</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Art Direction</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Graphic Design</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Copy Writing</span></h6>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Information Graphics</span>[/column]</h6>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;', 'WHAT WE DO', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'what-we-do', '', '', '2012-06-13 12:46:26', '2012-06-13 16:46:26', '', '0', 'http://getthepeople.com/?page_id=1274', '0', 'page', '', '0' ); ";i:543;s:290:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1275', '1', '2012-05-04 18:50:00', '2012-05-04 18:50:00', '', 'What We Do', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1274-revision', '', '', '2012-05-04 18:50:00', '2012-05-04 18:50:00', '', '1274', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1275', '0', 'revision', '', '0' ); ";i:544;s:3321:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1276', '1', '2012-05-04 18:50:15', '2012-05-04 18:50:15', '<div class=\"intro\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1620\" title=\"Header_OurProcess\" src=\"http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Header_OurProcess.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"940\" height=\"220\" /></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<h2>DISCOVER + EXPLORE</h2>\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=two-third-last ]\r\n\r\n<strong>Let\'s build a relationship.</strong> We want to know you and your business from the inside out. We\'ll take a journey to explore where you\'ve been, where you want to go, and who should know you when you get there. Asking the \'right\' questions and truly understanding your needs from the start is the foundation to a productive and lasting relationship.[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<h2>STRATEGY + CONCEPT</h2>\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=two-third-last ]\r\n\r\n<strong>We won\'t settle for just any design solution.</strong> Strategic thinking drives the planning phase – leading us to the best ways to achieve your goals and deliver solid customer experiences. We compile everything from the discovery phase to create a detailed road-map of where we\'re going and how we plan to get there. Through creative concepts and a butt-load of brainstorming we\'ll craft tailored solutions to deliver your content and message.[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<h2>DESIGN + REVIEW</h2>\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=two-third-last ]\r\n\r\n<strong>Now the rubber hits the road.</strong> Creative juices start to flow and what used to be ideas now begins to take shape and materialize into visual solutions. We\'ll continue to conceptualize, refine and perfect the creative direction until we all get that exciting twinkle in our eye that says \'that\'s the one\'. We\'ll make sure it leaves a lasting impression, stands out from the rest, and captivates your audience – keeping you looking smart and progressive.\r\n\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<h2>BUILD + TEST</h2>\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=two-third-last ]\r\n\r\n<strong>A beautifully designed website can only take you so far.</strong> We take an inventive approach to problem solving to find the best technical solutions to support the design, functional needs, and back-end management of your content. The functionality, structure and performance of our websites always meet W3C standards – search engine friendly and free from glitches and bugs. Finally, we test everything, then we test it again, and again...and again.\r\n\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<h2>LET ER FLY!</h2>\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=two-third-last ]\r\n\r\n<strong>Packaged and ready to go, it\'s time to launch.</strong> Proper planning and the right execution are the key to a successful launch. In this phase we’ll unveil the newest addition to your business and marketing efforts. We\'ll be there until the end to make sure everything takes off as planned, making any adjustments and tweaks along the way.\r\n\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'OUR PROCESS', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'our-process', '', '', '2012-06-13 12:44:15', '2012-06-13 16:44:15', '', '0', 'http://getthepeople.com/?page_id=1276', '0', 'page', '', '0' ); ";i:545;s:290:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1277', '1', '2012-05-04 18:50:07', '2012-05-04 18:50:07', '', 'Auto Draft', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1276-revision', '', '', '2012-05-04 18:50:07', '2012-05-04 18:50:07', '', '1276', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1277', '0', 'revision', '', '0' ); ";i:546;s:293:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1278', '1', '2012-05-04 18:50:15', '2012-05-04 18:50:15', '', 'Our Process', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1276-revision-2', '', '', '2012-05-04 18:50:15', '2012-05-04 18:50:15', '', '1276', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1278', '0', 'revision', '', '0' ); ";i:547;s:547:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1279', '1', '2011-10-03 12:18:58', '2011-10-03 12:18:58', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec ac purus nec diam laoreet sollicitudin. Fusce ullamcorper imperdiet turpis, non accumsan enim egestas in. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.\n\n[contact-form 1 \"Contact form 1\"] ', 'Contact', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '7-revision', '', '', '2011-10-03 12:18:58', '2011-10-03 12:18:58', '', '7', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1279', '0', 'revision', '', '0' ); ";i:548;s:274:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1280', '1', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', ' ', '', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '1280', '', '', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', '', '0', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1280', '3', 'nav_menu_item', '', '0' ); ";i:549;s:274:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1281', '1', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', ' ', '', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '1281', '', '', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', '', '0', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1281', '2', 'nav_menu_item', '', '0' ); ";i:550;s:274:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1282', '1', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', ' ', '', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '1282', '', '', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', '', '0', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1282', '4', 'nav_menu_item', '', '0' ); ";i:551;s:274:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1283', '1', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', ' ', '', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '1283', '', '', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', '2012-05-04 18:51:59', '', '0', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1283', '1', 'nav_menu_item', '', '0' ); ";i:552;s:301:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1297', '1', '2012-05-04 19:03:40', '2012-05-04 19:03:40', '', 'LifeSpace Home Slider', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1295-revision', '', '', '2012-05-04 19:03:40', '2012-05-04 19:03:40', '', '1295', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1297', '0', 'revision', '', '0' ); ";i:553;s:4697:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1298', '1', '2012-05-04 19:08:35', '2012-05-04 19:08:35', '<strong>BRAND DEVELOPMENT + LOGO DESIGN + WEB REDESIGN + SITE ARCHITECTURE + CONTENT DEVELOPMENT + COPY WRITING + HOW IT WORKS TUTORIALS + EMAIL MARKETING </strong>\r\n\r\nLifeSpace is a membership-based online application that allows people to manage all their life’s goals in one place. The site has over 15,000 registered users and consists of hundreds of pages, custom articles, pre-designed goal templates and tens-of-thousands user-created goals.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><a title=\"LifeSpace\" href=\"http://lifespace.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>VISIT SITE</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"intro\">CHALLENGE</div>\r\nA very small percentage of LifeSpace’s 15,000 registered users were actually returning to the site after their initial sign up. Additionally, the number of new registrations dropped off drastically after the site’s launch. LifeSpace was originally created on a custom-built platform with a patchwork of functionally and designed with no real brand identity or site strategy. The clear need was to make some serious changes for LifeSpace to become visually appealing, easy to use and on par with other member-based community websites.\r\n<div class=\"intro\">SOLUTION - Branding life and inspiration into how we achieve goals</div>\r\nLifeSpace needed LIFE. In order for LifeSpace to grow into a nationally and even internationally known application for creating and tracking goals it would need a total makeover and overhaul of the entire brand, site content, design and overall user experience.\r\n\r\nWe started by focusing on the brand development and creating a voice and visual identity that was fun, motivational and engaging. We accomplished this in a number of ways from creating a new logo, color schemes, custom graphics, fonts, buttons, calls-to-action, inspiring imagery, and consistent visual experience throughout the entire web application.\r\n\r\nThe next phase was to tackle what we felt was the largest issue, the flow and overall lack of organization of the content. We redesigned the entire flow and structure of the site from top to bottom, consolidating hundreds of pages of content, making it more dynamic, interactive, and intuitive to use.\r\n<h5>BRANDING</h5>\r\nWe organized the LifeSpace platform to focus on the main areas of a user’s life. We named and branded these ‘lifespaces’ by following an extensive process to create custom icons, color schemes and consistent imagery for each lifespace – bringing a visually inspirational component to the user experience.\r\n<h5>INTERNAL USER INTERFACE</h5>\r\nThe goal of the internal site was really showcase all the functionality of the website while keeping it simple and easy to use. We created a highly functioning, customizable, super powered dashboard we dubbed the SUERPAGE. It’s the one place where you can see, create, manage, track and share all your goals. We added a tab system so users can easily go from easy check lists, to calendar view, public discussions, and personal journal entries for each goal.\r\n<h5>COPY</h5>\r\nFresh copy writing was applied to the entire LifeSpace platform to truly communicate and reflect the new brand voice. We wrote the copy for the new external public website as well as the internal member-facing site to embody the new brand voice and identity.\r\n<h5>HOW IT WORKS TUTORIALS</h5>\r\nWe created a variety of fun and visual ‘How it Works’ presentations throughout the LifeSpace website. We felt it was important to create quick glance tutorials that would easily explain the power of what a user can accomplish with the online application.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote>\"GetThePeople played a huge role in getting my company to the next level.  They took many complicated and disconnected ideas from a pre-existing platform and turned them into a visually engaging design and a highly intuitive workflow.\r\n\r\nThey stuck with the project all the way through and consistently brought passion, creativity and fun to an otherwise overwhelming process. Thanks so much Megan and Rad for all you did and I can\'t wait to see what we can do together in the future!\" -- Greg Ausley, Founder of<a title=\"LifeSpace\" href=\"http://lifespace.com/\"> LifeSpace.com</a></blockquote>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\":1hr\" data-tooltip=\"Show trimmed content\"><img src=\"https://mail.google.com/mail/images/cleardot.gif\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>', 'LifeSpace', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'lifespace', '', '', '2012-05-21 15:22:30', '2012-05-21 19:22:30', '', '0', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1298', '1', 'post', '', '0' ); ";i:554;s:414:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1300', '1', '2012-05-04 19:07:48', '2012-05-04 19:07:48', '', 'LifeSpace-Branding-Inferface-Design-2', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'lifespace-branding-inferface-design-2', '', '', '2012-05-04 19:07:48', '2012-05-04 19:07:48', '', '1298', 'http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/LifeSpace-Branding-Inferface-Design-2.jpg', '2', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0' ); ";i:555;s:414:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1301', '1', '2012-05-04 19:07:53', '2012-05-04 19:07:53', '', 'LifeSpace-Branding-Inferface-Design-3', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'lifespace-branding-inferface-design-3', '', '', '2012-05-04 19:07:53', '2012-05-04 19:07:53', '', '1298', 'http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/LifeSpace-Branding-Inferface-Design-3.jpg', '3', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0' ); ";i:556;s:414:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1302', '1', '2012-05-04 19:07:59', '2012-05-04 19:07:59', '', 'LifeSpace-Branding-Inferface-Design-4', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'lifespace-branding-inferface-design-4', '', '', '2012-05-04 19:07:59', '2012-05-04 19:07:59', '', '1298', 'http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/LifeSpace-Branding-Inferface-Design-4.jpg', '4', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0' ); ";i:557;s:414:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1303', '1', '2012-05-04 19:08:03', '2012-05-04 19:08:03', '', 'LifeSpace-Branding-Inferface-Design-5', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'lifespace-branding-inferface-design-5', '', '', '2012-05-04 19:08:03', '2012-05-04 19:08:03', '', '1298', 'http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/LifeSpace-Branding-Inferface-Design-5.jpg', '5', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0' ); ";i:558;s:414:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1304', '1', '2012-05-04 19:08:07', '2012-05-04 19:08:07', '', 'LifeSpace-Branding-Inferface-Design-6', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'lifespace-branding-inferface-design-6', '', '', '2012-05-04 19:08:07', '2012-05-04 19:08:07', '', '1298', 'http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/LifeSpace-Branding-Inferface-Design-6.jpg', '6', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0' ); ";i:559;s:289:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1305', '1', '2012-05-04 19:06:50', '2012-05-04 19:06:50', '', 'LifeSpace', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1298-revision', '', '', '2012-05-04 19:06:50', '2012-05-04 19:06:50', '', '1298', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1305', '0', 'revision', '', '0' ); ";i:560;s:2702:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1306', '1', '2012-05-04 19:10:05', '2012-05-04 19:10:05', '<strong>BRANDING + ECOMMERCE + WEB DESIGN + CONTENT DEVELOPMENT</strong> <strong>+ SEO</strong>\r\n\r\nPrimoMaestroItalia (PMI) is a high-end Italian lighting company specializing in artistic, artisan-crafted lighting made in Florence, Italy. Their designs and products embody the Italian passion – capturing the finest details and made of the highest quality. They combine centuries-old craftsmanship with state-of-the-art lighting systems to deliver timeless, illuminated additions to one\'s life and home.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"> <a title=\"PrimoMaestro Italia\" href=\"http://primomaestro.com\" target=\"_blank\">VISIT SITE</a></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"intro\">CHALLENGE</div>\r\nPrimoMaestro Italia was looking to establish their brand presence and sell their products online in the US and internationally. They came to us with the desire to have a visually impactful brand and engaging website that would help increase their visibility in the marketplace and help generate leads and sales. Their vision was to target consumers as well as interior designers and architects who value and require luxurious and artful lighting. They wanted to create a premium online shopping experience, wrapped in the romance of the Italian culture.\r\n<div class=\"intro\">SOLUTION</div>\r\nIn order to set PrimoMaestro Italia apart from some of the more standard lighting companies, we approached the presentation of the lights in a way that supports the idea that each light is both functional and a work of art. So rather than simply grouping products into standard categories – table, floor, chandelier, we focused on featuring the various collections of lights as an art gallery would.\r\n\r\nWe developed the visual direction so that it was clear to visitors that this is a premium brand – focusing on highlighting the innovation, craftsmanship, and Italian origins. The design and overall look and feel would have to embody a clean and elegant style, with a smart balance of modern and classic elements.\r\n\r\nWe then applied the design and built a complete e-commerce shopping cart for both the English and Italian language websites. The website was built on a Content Management System that offers full online business capabilities – integrated shipping, payment gateways, email hosting, social media, reports and analytics, email marketing, CRM and contact form builder.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'PrimoMaestro Italia', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'primomaestro-italia', '', '', '2012-06-26 18:11:48', '2012-06-26 22:11:48', '', '0', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1306', '2', 'post', '', '0' ); ";i:561;s:438:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1307', '1', '2012-05-04 19:09:24', '2012-05-04 19:09:24', '', 'PrimoMaestro-branding-ecommerce-web-design-1', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'primomaestro-branding-ecommerce-web-design-1-2', '', '', '2012-05-04 19:09:24', '2012-05-04 19:09:24', '', '1306', 'http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/PrimoMaestro-branding-ecommerce-web-design-11.jpg', '1', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0' ); ";i:562;s:435:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1308', '1', '2012-05-04 19:09:29', '2012-05-04 19:09:29', '', 'PrimoMaestro-branding-ecommerce-web-design-2', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'primomaestro-branding-ecommerce-web-design-2', '', '', '2012-05-04 19:09:29', '2012-05-04 19:09:29', '', '1306', 'http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/PrimoMaestro-branding-ecommerce-web-design-2.jpg', '2', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0' ); ";i:563;s:435:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1309', '1', '2012-05-04 19:09:35', '2012-05-04 19:09:35', '', 'PrimoMaestro-branding-ecommerce-web-design-3', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'primomaestro-branding-ecommerce-web-design-3', '', '', '2012-05-04 19:09:35', '2012-05-04 19:09:35', '', '1306', 'http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/PrimoMaestro-branding-ecommerce-web-design-3.jpg', '3', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0' ); ";i:564;s:435:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1310', '1', '2012-05-04 19:09:39', '2012-05-04 19:09:39', '', 'PrimoMaestro-branding-ecommerce-web-design-4', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'primomaestro-branding-ecommerce-web-design-4', '', '', '2012-05-04 19:09:39', '2012-05-04 19:09:39', '', '1306', 'http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/PrimoMaestro-branding-ecommerce-web-design-4.jpg', '5', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0' ); ";i:565;s:2718:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1634', '1', '2012-06-26 18:06:31', '2012-06-26 22:06:31', '<strong>BRANDING + ECOMMERCE + WEB DESIGN + CONTENT DEVELOPMENT</strong> <strong>+ SEO</strong>\r\n\r\nPrimoMaestroItalia (PMI) is a high-end Italian lighting company specializing in artistic, artisan-crafted lighting made in Florence, Italy. Their designs and products embody the Italian passion – capturing the finest details and made of the highest quality. They combine centuries-old craftsmanship with state-of-the-art lighting systems to deliver timeless, illuminated additions to one\'s life and home.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"> <a title=\"PrimoMaestro Italia\" href=\"http://primomaestro.com\" target=\"_blank\">VISIT SITE</a></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"intro\">CHALLENGE</div>\r\nPrimoMaestro Italia was looking to establish their brand presence and sell their products online in the US and internationally. They came to us with the desire to have a visually impactful brand and engaging website that would help increase their visibility in the marketplace and help generate leads and sales. Their vision was to target consumers as well as interior designers and architects who value and require luxurious and artful lighting. They wanted to create a premium online shopping experience, wrapped in the romance of the Italian culture.\r\n<div class=\"intro\">SOLUTION</div>\r\nIn order to set PrimoMaestro Italia apart from some of the more standard lighting companies, we approached the presentation of the lights in a way that supports the idea that each light is both functional and a work of art. So rather than simply grouping products into standard categories – table, floor, chandelier, we focused on featuring the various collections of lights as an art gallery would.\r\n\r\nWe developed the visual direction so that it was clear to visitors that this is a premium brand – focusing on highlighting the innovation, craftsmanship, and Italian origins. The design and overall look and feel would have to embody a clean and elegant style, with a smart balance of modern and classic elements.\r\n\r\nWe then applied the design and built a complete e-commerce shopping cart for both the English and Italian language websites. The website was built on a Content Management System that offers full online business capabilities – integrated shipping, payment gateways, email hosting, social media, reports and analytics, email marketing, CRM and contact form builder.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'PrimoMaestro Italia', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '1306-revision-11', '', '', '2012-06-26 18:06:31', '2012-06-26 22:06:31', '', '1306', 'http://getthepeople.com/1306-revision-11/', '0', 'revision', '', '0' ); ";i:566;s:299:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1312', '1', '2012-05-04 19:09:08', '2012-05-04 19:09:08', '', 'PrimoMaestro Italia', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1306-revision', '', '', '2012-05-04 19:09:08', '2012-05-04 19:09:08', '', '1306', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1312', '0', 'revision', '', '0' ); ";i:567;s:568:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1520', '1', '2012-05-23 16:12:28', '2012-05-23 20:12:28', '<a href=\"http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/GTP_Graf_11.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1521\" title=\"GTP_Graf_1\" src=\"http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/GTP_Graf_11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"940\" height=\"300\" /></a>', 'GTP Graffiti Slider', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'gtp-graffiti-slider', '', '', '2012-05-23 16:15:33', '2012-05-23 20:15:33', '', '0', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1520', '0', 'post', '', '0' ); ";i:568;s:291:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1338', '1', '2012-05-04 19:08:35', '2012-05-04 19:08:35', '', 'LifeSpace', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1298-revision-2', '', '', '2012-05-04 19:08:35', '2012-05-04 19:08:35', '', '1298', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1338', '0', 'revision', '', '0' ); ";i:569;s:2183:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1314', '1', '2012-05-04 19:21:11', '2012-05-04 19:21:11', '<strong>STRATEGY + BRANDING + LOGO DESIGN + WEBSITE  REDESIGN + CONTENT DEVELOPMENT + PRINT</strong>\r\n\r\nShe Creates Change empowers women to create a career where they are fully engaged in life, claim their calling, and make a meaningful contribution in the world. Offering life changing programs, seminars, classes and intense retreats, SCC provides the tools and supportive community to help woman blossom and live authentically in both their personal and professional lives.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><a title=\"She Creates Change\" href=\"http://shecreateschange.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>VISIT SITE</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"intro\">CHALLENGE</div>\r\nShe Creates Change was seeking a full over-hall of the existing brand and website. There was an overall lack of any real brand identity or visual presentation. The desire was to create a logo and website that\'s look and feel reflects the fiery strength, confidence and ever changing woman of She Creates Change.\r\n<div class=\"intro\">SOLUTION – FIERY. FEMININE. FEARLESS.</div>\r\nWe worked closely with them to craft a brand that would not only appeal to a very niche demographic of women, but also embody the very spirit the organization is built upon. The logo features the full-bloom of the butterfly, which defines the work She Creates Change does to help women fully develop both personally and professionally. Content development was a large focus for the homepage, where we crafted a slider presentation featuring the women of change and the questions they find themselves asking at the major crossroads of their professional life.\r\n\r\nA CMS based website was built from the ground up to support their need to fully manage and easily update their website in-house. We also created press kits, marketing materials and promotional items in order to create unity across all touchpoints.', 'She Creates Change', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'she-creates-change', '', '', '2012-05-21 17:30:05', '2012-05-21 21:30:05', '', '0', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1314', '3', 'post', '', '0' ); ";i:570;s:420:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1315', '1', '2012-05-04 19:20:11', '2012-05-04 19:20:11', '', 'SheCreatesChange-branding-web-design-1', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '',