eeping you looking smart and progressive.\r\n\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n\r\nBUILD + TEST\r\n\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=two-third-last ]\r\n\r\nA beautifully designed website can only take you so far. We take an inventive approach to problem solving to find the best technical solutions to support the design, functional needs, and back-end management of your content. The functionality, structure and performance of our websites always meet W3C standards – search engine friendly and free from glitches and bugs. Finally, we test everything, then we test it again, and again...and again.\r\n\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n\r\nLET ER FLY!\r\n\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=two-third-last ]\r\n\r\nPackaged and ready to go, it\'s time to launch. Proper planning and the right execution are the key to a successful launch. In this phase we’ll unveil the newest addition to your business and marketing efforts. We\'ll be there until the end to make sure everything takes off as planned, making any adjustments and tweaks along the way.\r\n\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'OUR PROCESS', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1276-revision-8', '', '', '2012-05-04 19:52:18', '2012-05-04 19:52:18', '', '1276', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=1335', '0', 'revision', '', '0' ); ";i:592;s:4767:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1369', '1', '2012-06-13 12:29:25', '2012-06-13 16:29:25', '&nbsp;\n\n<a href=\"http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Header_WhoWeAre1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1613\" title=\"Header_WhoWeAre\" src=\"http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Header_WhoWeAre1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"940\" height=\"289\" /></a>\n<div class=\"intro\" dir=\"ltr\">GetThePeople is a full service creative design studio based in New York City.  <strong class=\"intro\" dir=\"ltr\"></strong></div>\n[column width=two-third ]\n\nWe’re a tight-knit team with broad experience in branding, web development, and strategic marketing. We build close relationships with each client making their wins, our wins. From emerging start-ups to major players, we partner with those ready to push their edge and elevate their brand and online experience.\n\nA broad understanding of the drivers in business, art, music, industry trends, coupled with a complete obsession with the creative world and where it\'s going, is what we bake into every project. We make it our job to deliver compelling creative solutions rather than simply executing tasks. Hey, its our life\'s work. Constantly striving to push creative that is not only aesthetically pleasing, but also has purpose and strategic reason for communicating your content in a way that’s relevant.\n\n[/column]\n\n[column width=one-third-last ]\n\n<a href=\"http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/GTP_Tag.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1589\" title=\"GTP_Tag\" src=\"http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/GTP_Tag.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"243\" /></a>\n\n[/column]\n\n&nbsp;\n<div class=\"intro\"> THE TEAM</div>\n[column width=two-third ]\n\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1538\" title=\"Team_Rad\" src=\"http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Team_Rad.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"320\" />\n\n[/column]\n\n[column width=one-third-last ]\n<h3>Rad Bratich</h3>\n<h5><span style=\"color: #808080;\">Founding Partner + Lead Creative</span></h5>\nRad is, well...<strong><em> rad!</em></strong> As the Founding Partner and Chief Creative Officer he is a miracle worker and perfectionist to say the least. A true artist with an obsession for all things creative: design, art, music, architecture, tattoos, street culture, fashion – Rad is the visionary that <em><strong>is</strong></em> GetThePeople. With 15 years in the industry as lead designer and creative director, he oversees all strategy, creative direction, and design – all the while multi-tasking as the company DJ. He can draw a perfect circle with one line, desk-drum every Clash song, inspire the uninspired and is always down for a good laugh.\n\n[/column]\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1580\" title=\"divider_diagonal\" src=\"http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/divider_diagonal.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"940\" height=\"10\" />\n\n[column width=one-third ]\n<h3>Megan Murphy</h3>\n<h5><span style=\"color: #808080;\">Founding Partner – New Business + Strategy</span></h5>\nChief of Fun and head of New Business &amp; Strategy. That means making our clients lives\' easier and ensuring that each project\'s goals are met on time and within budget. With a background in online marketing and creative strategy, she oversees all content development, branding and online web strategies. Megan sets the stage for our open, family-style culture. Passionate entrepreneur, foodie, yogi, hugger, dancer, boxer, mega-manifester, femme fatale...lets face it, she\'s the HBIC.\n\n[/column]\n\n[column width=two-third-last ]\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1560\" title=\"Team_Meagn\" src=\"http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Team_Meagn.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"320\" />\n\n[/column]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n<div class=\"intro\">BACK IN THE DAY</div>\nLet\'s rewind. A dozen years ago, GetThePeople was nothing more than a subway train conversation. It all began with an obsession of art and graffiti, combined with a desire to spread and share new creative concepts instead of simply bombing \"tags\".\n\nThe words GetThePeople were sprayed, inked, stamped, stenciled, and stickered all over the streets of New York City. After years of visibility, the work graduated into a more graphic and strategic design application, finally transitioning into the lifelong dream - a creative design studio.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[uds-billboard name=\"GTP Graf\"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;', 'WHO WE ARE', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1272-autosave', '', '', '2012-06-13 12:29:25', '2012-06-1