 brand.\r\n\r\nWe compile everything – your name, mission statements, the products and services you provide, and how you deliver them to create a specific image in your target market\'s mind. Its that perceived image of your company, combined with an emotional connection that motivates your audience to choose you above all the rest.[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<h2> WEB</h2>\r\nYour website. Its the single greatest opportunity for your business to interact with the world, communicate powerful messages, declare your presence, and differentiate your brand from the rest. This is a big friggin\' deal. All your marketing and communication efforts lead back to this one spot. So while we craft strategic plans and are serious about premium design, creating websites that can transform your business and relationships is what makes us tick. Its the experience your website provides that stays with visitors. Whether it\'s pushing your brand to the next level, increasing sales, building relationships, or bringing a new business to market, pushing the edge with your website is your best chance at achieving your online goals.[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third-last ]\r\n<h2>CREATIVE STRATEGY</h2>\r\nStrategic thinking and creative insights are the nuts and bolts of our shop. We partner directly with you and get to the heart of your marketing goals and challenges to create short-term wins and long-term road-maps. Nailing down a proper strategy can lead to improved reputation, increased consumer loyalty and greater profitability. Move ahead without one, and problems could occur down the road if competitors do a better job of it than you do. We\'ll stick to this game-plan every step of the way, constantly refining and upgrading how we intend to execute and deliver effective user experiences.[/column]', 'WHAT WE DO', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1274-revision-8', '', '', '2012-05-07 15:47:24', '2012-05-07 15:47:24', '', '1274', 'http://getthepeople.com/?p=13