ing</li>\r\n	<li>Information Graphics[/column]</li>\r\n</ul>', 'WHAT WE DO', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1274-revision-19', '', '', '2012-05-07 16:20:39', '2012-05-07 16:20:39', '', '1274', 'http://getthepeople.com/1274-revision-19/', '0', 'revision', '', '0' ); ";i:636;s:335:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1511', '1', '2012-05-23 15:54:10', '2012-05-23 19:54:10', '', 'GTP_Graf_2', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'gtp_graf_2', '', '', '2012-05-23 15:54:10', '2012-05-23 19:54:10', '', '1272', 'http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/GTP_Graf_2.jpg', '2', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0' ); ";i:637;s:1456:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1377', '1', '2012-05-07 19:09:03', '2012-05-07 19:09:03', '<strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">BRANDING + MOBILE INTERFACE DESIGN + LOGO + WEB DESIGN</span></strong>\r\n\r\nNov8rix is a NYC-based mobile technology company that makes it easy to brand your own iPhone or Android app. Supporting all media formats, the platform allows you to populate it with your own content. A turn-key product for any individual or organization to looking have their own mobile app.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"intro\">CHALLENGE</div>\r\nAs a tech start-up, Nov8rix had strong team of tech savvy engineers and super powered coders, but were lacking any creative edge or visual direction. They realized that in order to launch a mobile app company along with three new apps, they needed a strong brand, website, and mobile interface design.\r\n<div class=\"intro\">SOLUTION</div>\r\nA branding direction focusing on the modern, futuristic appeal of mobile technology was developed and applied to the website and all marketing materials. From there we designed and developed the graphic interface for the company\'s flagship product, including a branded web-based admin. We also designed the interface of two additional iphone apps, iSarge and SearchPad.', 'Nov8rix', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nov8rix', '', '', '2012-05-23 14:40:07'