pleasing, but also has purpose and strategic reason for communicating your content in a way that’s relevant for years to come.\r\n<div class=\"intro\">BACK IN THE DAY</div>\r\nLet\'s rewind. A dozen years ago, GetThePeople was nothing more than a subway train conversation. It all began with an obsession of art and graffiti, combined with a desire to spread and share new creative concepts instead of simply bombing \"tags\".\r\n\r\nThe words GetThePeople were sprayed, inked, stamped, stenciled, and stickered all over the streets of New York City. After years of visibility, the work graduated into a more graphic and strategic design application, finally transitioning into the lifelong dream - a creative design studio.[/column]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/GTP_LegacyMatrix_3.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-1372 alignleft\" title=\"GTP_LegacyMatrix_3\" src=\"http://getthepeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/GTP_LegacyMatrix_3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"576\" height=\"311\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Who We Are', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1272-revision-7', '', '', '2012-05-07 16:43:46', '2012-05-07 16:43:46', '', '1272', 'http://getthepeople.com/1272-revision-7/', '0', 'revision', '', '0' ); ";i:646;s:3814:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1387', '1', '2012-05-07 17:26:21', '2012-05-07 17:26:21', '<div class=\"intro\">We create online design experiences that lead to actionable and measurable results. Well crafted solutions – soup to nuts.</div>\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<h2>SMART BRANDING</h2>\r\n<div class=\"intro\">Your brand is how you tell the story of your business. It is the idea and gut feeling your audience has about your company.</div>\r\nIt\'s the personality, character, and reputation a business carries with everything they do. While a logo, typefaces and color schemes are super important, they\'re only a fraction of what it takes to create a great brand.\r\n\r\nWe compile everything – your name, mission statements, the products and services you provide, and how you deliver them to create a specific image in your target market\'s mind.\r\n\r\nIts that perceived image of your company, combined with an emotional connection that motivates your audience to choose you above all the rest.[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<h2> PROGRESSIVE WEB DESIGN</h2>\r\n<div class=\"intro\">Your website is the single greatest opportunity for your business to interact with the world and declare your online presence.</div>\r\nYour website allows you to communicate powerful messages that can differentiate your brand from the rest. This is a big friggin\' deal. All your marketing and communication efforts lead back to this one spot. So while we craft strategic plans and are serious about premium design, creating websites that can transform your business and relationships is what makes us tick.\r\n\r\nIts the experience your website provides that stays with visitors. Whether it\'s pushing your brand to the next level, increasing sales, building relationships, or bringing a new business to market, pushing the edge with your website is your best chance at achieving your online goals.[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third-last ]\r\n<h2>CREATIVE STRATEGY</h2>\r\n<div class=\"intro\">Without a solid strategy your end result ends up patch work and afterthoughts. Strategy before design turns visions into real solutions.</div>\r\nStrategic thinking and creative insights are the nuts and bolts of our shop. We partner directly with you and get to the heart of your marketing goals and challenges to create short-term wins and long-term road-maps.\r\n\r\nNailing down a proper strategy can lead to improved reputation, increased consumer loyalty and greater profitability. Move ahead without one, and problems could occur down the road if competitors do a better job of it than you do.\r\n\r\nWe\'ll stick to this game-plan every step of the way, constantly refining and upgrading how we intend to execute and deliver effective user experiences.[/column]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"intro\" style=\"text-align: left;\">AREAS OF EXPERTISE + KEY SERVICES</div>\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Identity Development</li>\r\n	<li>Brand Voice</li>\r\n	<li>Positioning</li>\r\n	<li>Visual Identity</li>\r\n	<li>Message Strategy</li>\r\n	<li>Logo Design[/column]</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Web Design</li>\r\n	<li>Development</li>\r\n	<li>E-commerce</li>\r\n	<li>Search Engine Optimization</li>\r\n	<li>Social Media Integration</li>\r\n	<li>Content Management System[/column]</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[column width=one-third-last ]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Content Development</li>\r\n	<li>Online Marketing</li>\r\n	<li>Art Direction</li>\r\n	<li>Graphic Design</li>\r\n	<li>Copy Writing</li>\r\n	<li>Information Graphics[/column]</li>\r\n</ul>', 'WHAT WE DO', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1274-revision-20', '', '', '2012-05-07 17:26:21', '2012-05-07 17:26:21', '', '1274', 'http://getthepeople.com/1274-revision-20/', '0', 'revision', '', '0' ); ";i:647;s:3218:"INSERT INTO wp_gtpposts VALUES( '1389', '1', '2012-05-07 16:21:55', '2012-05-07 16:21:55', '<div id=\"internal-source-marker_0.5772074327428007\" class=\"intro\" dir=\"ltr\">Beautiful, innovative design doesn’t happen by accident –– its planned. And having an air-tight process holds the course.</div>\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<h3>DISCOVER + EXPLORE</h3>\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=two-third-last ]\r\n\r\nLet\'s build a relationship. We want to know you and your business from the inside out. We\'ll take a journey to explore where you\'ve been, where you want to go, and who should know you when you get there. Asking the \'right\' questions and truly understanding your needs from the start is the foundation to a productive and lasting relationship.[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<h3>STRATEGY + CONCEPT</h3>\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=two-third-last ]\r\n\r\nWe won\'t settle for just any solution. Strategic thinking drives the planning phase – leading us to the best ways to achieve your goals and deliver solid customer experiences. We compile everything from the discovery phase to create a detailed road-map of where we\'re going and how we plan to get there. Through creative concepts and a butt-load of brainstorming we\'ll craft tailored solutions to deliver your content and message.[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<h3>DESIGN+ REVIEW</h3>\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=two-third-last ]\r\n\r\nNow the rubber hits the road. Creative juices start to flow and what used to be ideas now begins to take shape and materialize into visual solutions. We\'ll continue to conceptualize, refine and perfect the creative direction until we all get that exciting twinkle in our eye that says \'that\'s the one\'. We\'ll make sure it leaves a lasting impression, stands out from the rest, and captivates your audience – keeping you looking smart and progressive.\r\n\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<h3>BUILD + TEST</h3>\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=two-third-last ]\r\n\r\nA beautifully designed website can only take you so far. We take an inventive approach to problem solving to find the best technical solutions to support the design, functional needs, and back-end management of your content. The functionality, structure and performance of our websites always meet W3C standards – search engine friendly and free from glitches and bugs. Finally, we test everything, then we test it again, and again...and again.\r\n\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=one-third ]\r\n<h3>LET ER FLY!</h3>\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column width=two-third-last ]\r\n\r\nPackaged and ready to go, it\'s time to launch. Proper planning and the right execution are the key to a successful launch. In this phase we’ll unveil the newest addition to your business and marketing efforts. We\'ll be there until the end to make sure everything takes off as planned, m